text:
1. I-80 westbound on-ramp at Castle Peak/Boreal Ridge: The on-ramp is CLOSED through 12:01 p.m. Friday, August 20. Westbound motorists are advised to use Donner Lake Interchange as a detour. 

Read more: https://t.co/apvn3pDNO7

@CHP_Truckee @CHPTruckeeScale @Caltrux @borealmtn https://t.co/n7Nr0Zus5B

#TrafficAlert: Maintenance crews will be performing roadway repairs on I-80 EB between Boca and Floriston. Motorists should expect a #2 lane closure between 7 p.m. tonight and 2 p.m. Thursday.

Read more: https://t.co/Pt8k9VbBB4

@CHP_Truckee @NevadaCountyCA https://t.co/HrOYqJdhwP

#TrafficAlert Eastbound U.S. 50 in West Sacramento is scheduled for 79-hour full closure 9 p.m. Friday, 6/13 until 4 a.m. Tuesday, 6/17.  Closure is from the Yolo I-80/US 50 connector ramp to Jefferson Blvd.
Click here for more information: https://t.co/dDF9BUW1tP
